rows.label: tlk45600171_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I needed to catch my breath after
experiencing such a historical moment.
A spot of prayer should do the trick.

rows.label: tlk45600171_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Really, I suppose I ought to go home
to Avaritia before I get mixed up in
any of this, but...I think I'll stick around.

rows.label: tlk45600171_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I only planned to come here on a lazy
tourist spree, but...my merchant blood
is telling me I have to see this through!
